# Progress

The "Progress" file tracks the journey of the current project from start to finish.
For each work session, the work, decisions, and outcomes are recorded, along with the phase that it happened in.
This file will accumulate the history of the project's journey from start to finish.

## File

`memory-bank/progress.md`

## How to Create

This file should be created when the first work session of a project is started.

## When to Update

When sufficient tasks in `memory-bank/tasks.md` have completed such that the `memory-bank/activeContext.md` is ready to be changed to a new focus, that information gets moved to a succint section in this file.
Each time this file is updated, a *new* section should be *appended* to the *bottom* of the file.

