    - Set up ESLint, Prettier, and basic lint/fmt scripts
    - Added initial folder structure: `src/`, `public/`, `types/`
    - Created basic HomePage and App shell components
    - Configured project for strict type checking
* Decisions made
    - Decided to use Vite for fast development and hot module replacement
    - Selected TypeScript strict mode to enforce better code quality

